ClassDriver:
Features - 
	* Time countdown once you start the game. You lose time when obstacles are hit. (Mandatory)
	* Bucky as a driver in a convertible car. (optional)
	* The end goal is on campus. Once the goal is reached it ends the game (Mandatory)
	* scoring is based on how many seconds you had left whenever the game ended. (Mandatory)
	* Records top score, and last run score. (Mandatory)
	* Move side to side with arrow keys (Mandatory)
  * performance it must be able to run on a phone (Mandatory)
  * must not allow double input. (Mandatory)
  * controls must be easy to use and understand (Mandatory)
  * victory and defeat must be  distinguishable through unique sound cues (Mandatory)
  * Changed the car that Bucky divers (optional)
